name: PDS TORNADO #5
description: The S.A.N.W.S office or offices in “Texarkana” and or “Kansas city, Lubbock, Hattiesburg, and Jackson ” have issued a “PDS TORNADO WATCH #5” at “1:48 PM EST”. primary threats to expect include “A couple dozen tornadoes of which some could be strong, gusty winds up to 80MPH, and hail up to 2 inches”. impact expect damage to “Vehicles, outdoor objects, homes, trees, and outdoor animals”. this “PDS TORNADO WATCH” will expire at “11:55 PM EST” on the “30th”.
